    public static class BoxFamily.ParticipantList<E>
extends com.google.common.collect.ForwardingList<E>
    A thread-safe, append-only list of observers/middleware. All modifications other than add() are forbidden.
    See Also:
    disable()

      • disable

        public void disable()
        Clear this list and prevent any further modifications to it. For example:

        box.getFamily().getChangeMiddlewares().disable();

        means that ChangeMiddleware can't be used on boxes in this family.
